summary:
- **Exploration Funding Approved**: $189,200 Queensland Government CEI grant for 3D geophysical surveys at Bajool Prospect (targeting porphyry Cu-Mo system).  
- **Drill Results**: Historical core re-assay highlights **16m @ 0.57% Cu & 441ppm Mo** (from 156m), including **2m @ 3.22% Cu & 252ppm Mo**.  
- **Project Acquisition Update**: Tranche 1 (51% acquisition) of Capricorn Project pending execution of native title access agreements.  

*No capital raising, trading halt, or material financial data disclosed.*
